    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend trip, this beauty is ready to go! It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is looking for a new home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
