      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six powerplant. This driver-spec example is equipped with a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive Double VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity. With individual throttle bodies providing sharp atmospheric induction and a suspension setup that remains taut through the apex, this M3 delivers a visceral, analog driving experience. Showing honest patina consistent with its age, it remains a robust platform for the discerning purist.",
